As NIGHTSHIFT got behind POLAR CLAW he began to back out keeping
himself between NIGHTSHIFT and the QUEEN.

&quot;Leaving so soon are we?&quot; She said as she noticed the movement.
&quot;Perhaps I am not ready for you to leave.&quot;

POLAR CLAW chuckled, &quot;We are not yours to command!&quot; He fired his
blaster at the two drones who were trying to pursue NIGHTSHIFT
knocking them both back. &quot;We may be small, but we still have a bite!&quot;

THE QUEEN hissed as she launched herself at POLAR CLAW!

RAMULUS, WOLFGANG and POLAR CLAW opened fire on the QUEEN their bright
bolts of energy converging on her.

&quot;Is that all you have?&quot; The QUEEN said with a shriek as she kept
moving forward, step by step.

POLAR CLAW said nothing as they all kept their blasts going. Meanwhile
through the opening in the cieling PROWL, in beast mode, came flying
in carrying a large vaguely spherical object in his claws.

Numbers were counting down on the face of it as PROWL positioned
himself above the hive!

15 . .  14 . . .  13 . . . the numbers on the face read as they counted down.

